{"data": [{"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "0_1734712018.693784", "card_id": "Q_6982007681", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 264}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "车主花 200 万买仰望 U9，在租给租车公司后被暴力拆解，具体情况如何？车主应该如何维权？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "近日，一位比亚迪仰望 U9 车主在网上发视频维权。他花费 200 万元买的仰望 U9，被租赁公司出租后遭到租车人的暴力拆解，本人已报警维权。200 万买的仰望 u9 出租后被暴力拆解，车主：已报警"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-450a6df268d77f9ae67c3e18283b571d_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "877 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/6982007681"}}, "attached_info": "CkEIiZDvtcGQwugaEAMaCTExMjM3MzE4MSD8l/66BjAAOIQGQAByCjY5ODIwMDc2ODF4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "1_1734712018.694576", "card_id": "Q_7312121313", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 53}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何评价 2024 年 12 月米哈游《原神》5.3 前瞻直播【炽烈的还魂诗】？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "[图片]"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-c8eb384e375037582768d814640abe34_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "158 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/7312121313"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIiZDvtcGQwugaEAMaCTExMjQzOTEyNiC3xJC7BjAAODtAAXIKNzMxMjEyMTMxM3gAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "2_1734712018.694913", "card_id": "Q_7293820415", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 21}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "女子在黑龙江雪乡玩「泼水成冰」失误致二级烫伤，这种玩法需要哪些条件？背后有什么科学原理？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "近日，一女子在哈尔滨雪乡旅游时模仿网上流行的「泼水成冰」玩，结果因操作失误导致头部二级烫伤。当事人江女士称，幸好自己是医护人员，懂得急救知识，拿雪冷敷了一两个小时，并去诊所敷了烫伤膏。 江女士称，之前在网上见过「泼水成冰」的景象，只要在极寒天气中泼出热水，水便会在空中迅速凝结成冰，她决定亲自尝试一下。然而由于她操作失误，热水扬起的弧线不但没有瞬间成冰，还浇在其头部导致烫伤。 奔流新闻记者注意到，在社交平台搜索「泼水成冰」相关的词条，能看到很多拍摄的照片和视频。其实，「泼水成冰」中的结冰并不是水结冰，而是水形成水蒸气之后，水蒸气在寒冷空气里凝结成水滴或者凝华成小冰晶，这种景象形成需要相应的气候条件。在未能达到「泼水就能成冰」的温度条件时，易发生被烫伤的情况。中国天气微博就曾发布提醒，「泼水成冰动作危险，请勿轻易尝试。」女子在哈尔滨雪乡玩「泼水成冰」失误致二级烫伤"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-83555266853ea17658370088659cea4f_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "115 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/7293820415"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIiZDvtcGQwugaEAMaCTExMjQzNTQ4OSC4xI+7BjAAOB5AAnIKNzI5MzgyMDQxNXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "3_1734712018.695507", "card_id": "Q_615419286", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 154}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么《BanG Dream! It's MyGO!!!!!》能收获如此众多的好评？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "54 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/615419286"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IiZDvtcGQwugaEAMaCDk5MDM5OTA3IOWlraYGMAA48gRAA3IJNjE1NDE5Mjg2eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "4_1734712018.695747", "card_id": "Q_24676400", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 43}, 