在美国没有销售任何路由器产品，且公司产品不存在网络安全漏洞。 用路由器发动网络袭击，这个说法真是令人哭笑不得，就像中国使馆之前所回应的，希望美相关部门在评估网络安全事件时应以充分证据为基础，而不是进行毫无根据的指控。 中美经贸合作互利共赢，造福两国人民。美方一贯标榜市场经济、公平竞争、自由贸易，如今所作所为，害人害己，不仅违背自己的原则，还扰乱全球产供链稳定，不符合任何一方利益。大蒜之后，美政府又盯上一款中国商品"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-b69ea178cbe17bd99d4678f8b7131e45_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "热度累计中", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/7290873287"}}, "attached_info": "CkEIiZDvtcGQwugaEAMaCTExMjQzNDg4OCC/tY+7BjAAOIICQBpyCjcyOTA4NzMyODd4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "27_1734712018.705411", "card_id": "Q_26076643", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 76}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "《千与千寻》里最后千寻是怎么知道那一群猪里没有自己的爸爸妈妈的呢?"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "我还是很想知道…"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-6743eb2f88bbf25eacf69f659d2223e5_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "热度累计中", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/26076643"}}, "attached_info": "Cj0IiZDvtcGQwugaEAMaBzI2MTM1MjIg/qGEogUwADjTAkAbcggyNjA3NjY0M3gAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "28_1734712018.705661", "card_id": "Q_5310199314", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 86}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "古希腊为啥比古中国发达那么多？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "我网上见过雅典卫城，很难想象古希腊人的数学水平，我感觉以建筑物对比，紫禁城太落后了吧！"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-395510db4816af3aa750c9252d9d168f_720w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "热度累计中", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu